4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT GENERALLY REVISING LAWS RELATED TO RECREATIONAL
5 VEHICLES; ALLOWING OFF-SITE DISPLAYS AND SALES IN CERTAIN LOCATIONS FOR CERTAIN
6 MOTOR VEHICLES; DEFINING "MOTOR VEHICLES"; AND AMENDING SECTION SECTIONS 61-4-123 AND
